                Therefore, I sincerely hope that, you will find Trust Overseas Recruiting Agency (TORA) as the best recruiting agent in Bangladesh whenever you need a qualified and experienced work force for your project. It will be highly appreciated if you please allow us an opportunity to establish a business relationship in future. We are cordially inviting you to see our capability to serve you the best by supplying manpower from Bangladesh.
            </p>
            <p>
